DelayedSimulation
public static class DelayedSimulation.LOTCompoundState
extends DelayedSimulation.LOSCompoundState

This class provides the compound state (s1, s2, a) or (s1, s2) where s1 is a state from a label-on-transition automaton A1, s2 is a state from a label-on-transition automaton A2, and a is a symbol in the alphabet. The objective is to test if A1 is simulated by A2.

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
